\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	1.	}\kerning1\expnd1\expndtw6
Download and install 
\f1\b GIT
\f0\b0  from {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://git-scm.com/download/win"}}{\fldrslt http://git-scm.com/download/win}} . Choose the second option so that GIT is added to your PATH.\
